Cordillera del Cóndor. Centro Shuar Yunkumas. Cerro Chunak Naint (Vulture Mountain in Shuar). Sandstone plateau, 1000-1270 m elevation, with dense forest. Permanent one-hectare forest inventory plot: Parcela Yunkumas. Trees > 10 cm DBH tagged and measured.
